snippet.title: 23 SMART LIFE HACKS FOR EVERY OCCASION
snippet.description:
Ways to make your life easier with these fantastic hacks. 

As we go through life, we come across little problems that seem unsolvable. But today, we’re going to show you some fun tricks you can try that will help save you time and hassle. Like when you have to sign a bunch of documents all at once. One way to fix that is to tape some pens on a piece of paper (Somewhat diagonally) and then use them to write. Now let’s head to the kitchen, where you need to make perfectly round crepes for your guests. You don’t need to buy an expensive crepe tool that flattens them out and turns them into a perfect circle — you just need a chopstick or a skewer instead. You break it in the middle, create a 90-degree angle, and voila. Did you know you can use an old highlighter to paint or write stuff down on your tablet? Watch the video to see how to do it.

1:04 — Perfectly round crepes
2:02 — No cake plates? Try this hack 
3:09 — Avoid staining your shirt collar with this trick 
5:08 — DIY fake nose ring 
6:16 — A way to cut package tape 
8:12 — DIY compass using three pencils

snippet.title: India's Republic Day Parade 26th January, 2021 - LIVE
snippet.description:
#RepublicDay Parade 2021 का सीधा प्रसारण | 26 January Parade Live
#RepublicDayparade #RepublicDay2021 #IndiaRepublicDay #गणतंत्रदिवस 
India celebrates her 72nd Republic Day on 26 January 2021. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 72nd Republic Day Parade - after our historic initiative in 2013 - on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the ninth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan.

snippet.title: FAU-G Game Exclusive First Look & Gameplay | Action Game | Weapons | Mission | First Impressions🔥🔥🔥
snippet.description:
Namaskaar Dosto, is video mein maine aapse baat ki hai FAU-G ke baare mein jaha pe is game ko announce kiya tha recently abhi PUBG Mobile ke recent India ban ke baad Mr. Akshay Kumar aur nCore Games ne. Yaha pe finally aaj 26th January 2021 ko Indian Republic Day ke mauke pe isi FAU-G Game ko launch kiya hai jaha yeh ek action packed game hai aur ise kehte hai Fearless And United Guards, yaha pe first mission Galwan valley clash pe based hai aur yaha pe future mein hume multiplayer aur free style ka bhi maja milega. Abhi yaha pe FAU-G merchandise ka bhi option hai aur kaafi sahi experience hai FAU-G game ka. Maine aapke saath isi game ki kuch details share ki hai aur share kiya hai ek exclusive gameplay isi FAU-G Game ka. India mein is game ke launch hone se pehle hi 5 Milllon downloads poore ho gaye the. Abhi bahut se log PUBG Mobile India ka bhi wait kar rahe hai lekin FAU-G ne phele aake ek tareek se baazi maar li hai. Maine aapse ek detailed gameplay aur overview share kiya hai isi FAUG Game ka jaha pe ek first release point of view se yeh ek bahut  accha experience hai. Mujhe umeed hai ki aapko FAU-G ke baare mein yeh video pasand aayegi.

snippet.title: Godzilla vs. Kong – Official Trailer
snippet.description:
In theaters and streaming exclusively on @HBOMax* March 26.
 
*Available on @HBOMax in the US only, for 31 days, at no extra cost to subscribers.

https://www.godzillavskong.com/
https://www.facebook.com/GodzillaVsKong
https://www.instagram.com/godzillavskong/
https://twitter.com/GodzillaVsKong

---

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures comes the long-awaited face-off between two icons, “Godzilla vs. Kong,” the next epic adventure in Legendary’s cinematic Monsterverse, directed by Adam Wingard.

Legends collide in “Godzilla vs. Kong” as these mythic adversaries meet in a spectacular battle for the ages, with the fate of the world hanging in the balance.  Kong and his protectors undertake a perilous journey to find his true home, and with them is Jia, a young orphaned girl with whom he has formed a unique and powerful bond.  But they unexpectedly find themselves in the path of an enraged Godzilla, cutting a swath of destruction across the globe.  The epic clash between the two titans—instigated by unseen forces—is only the beginning of the mystery that lies deep within the core of the Earth.

The film stars Alexander Skarsgård (“Big Little Lies,” “The Little Drummer Girl”), Millie Bobby Brown (“Stranger Things”), Rebecca Hall (“Christine,” “Professor Marston and the Wonder Women”), Brian Tyree Henry (“Joker,” “Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse”), Shun Oguri (“Weathering with You”), Eiza González (“Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw”), Julian Dennison (“Deadpool 2”), with Kyle Chandler (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”) and Demián Bichir (“The Nun,” “The Hateful Eight”).
Wingard (“The Guest,” “You’re Next”) directed from a screenplay by Eric Pearson (“Thor: Ragnarok”) and Max Borenstein (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters,” “Kong: Skull Island”), story by Terry Rossio (“Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales”) and Michael Dougherty & Zach Shields (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”), based on the character “Godzilla” owned and created by TOHO CO., LTD.  The film was produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric McLeod, Jon Jashni, Thomas Tull and Brian Rogers, with Jay Ashenfelter, Herbert W. Gains, Dan Lin, Roy Lee, Yoshimitsu Banno and Kenji Okuhira executive producing.

The director’s behind-the-scenes creative team included director of photography Ben Seresin (“The Mummy,” “World War Z”), production designers Owen Paterson (“Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle,” “Godzilla”) and Thomas S. Hammock (“Blair Witch”), editor Josh Schaeffer (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”), costume designer Ann Foley (“Skyscraper”) and visual effects supervisor John “DJ” DesJardin (upcoming “Zack Snyder’s Justice League”).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, “Godzilla vs. Kong.”  The film will be released nationwide in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX on March 26, 2021 and will be available in the U.S. on HBO Max for 31 days from theatrical release.  It is rated PG-13 for intense sequences of creature violence/destruction and brief language.

snippet.title: Republic Day Parade 2021
snippet.description:
#RepublicDay Parade 2021 का सीधा प्रसारण | 26 January Parade Live
#RepublicDayparade #RepublicDay2021 #IndiaRepublicDay #गणतंत्रदिवस 
India celebrates her 72nd Republic Day on 26 January 2021. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan, India's National Broadcaster to LIVE-STREAM the magnificent 72nd Republic Day Parade - after our historic initiative in 2013 - on our official channel on YouTube. www.youtube/DoordarshanNational. Doordarshan has been telecasting the Republic Day Parade LIVE since the early sixties when cameras and equipment had to be taken out of the existing studio for this event! Today, for the ninth consecutive year, we will LIVE-STREAM the Republic Day Parade. Proud Indians and Indophiles from all over the world will be watching, along with our viewers from the freezing climate of Leh to the remotest corners of Kanyakumari, Thank you for always being with us - Friends of Doordarshan. We at Doordarshan extend our warm regards to all Indians in the country as well as abroad. It is the proud privilege of Doordarshan.

Actor Makapa Anand has won many Vijay TV awards. The awards and the trophies are the extraordinary achievements of his life.

snippet.title: Disney's Raya and the Last Dragon | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
On March 5, join Raya on her quest to find the last dragon. See Disney’s Raya and the Last Dragon in theaters or order it on Disney+ with Premier Access on March 5. Learn more: http://disney.com/raya  

About Raya and the Last Dragon: 
 
“Raya and the Last Dragon” takes us on an exciting, epic journey to the fantasy world of Kumandra, where humans and dragons lived together long ago in harmony. But when an evil force threatened the land, the dragons sacrificed themselves to save humanity. Now, 500 years later, that same evil has returned and it’s up to a lone warrior, Raya, to track down the legendary last dragon to restore the fractured land and its divided people. However, along her journey, she’ll learn that it’ll take more than a dragon to save the world—it’s going to take trust and teamwork as well.

“Raya and the Last Dragon” features an outstanding voice cast, including Kelly Marie Tran as the voice of the intrepid warrior Raya; Awkwafina as the legendary dragon, Sisu; Gemma Chan as Raya’s nemesis, Namaari; Daniel Dae Kim as Raya’s visionary father, Benja; Sandra Oh as Namaari’s powerful mother, Virana; Benedict Wong as Tong, a formidable giant; Izaac Wang as Boun, a 10-year-old entrepreneur; Thalia Tran as the mischievous toddler Little Noi; Alan Tudyk as Tuk Tuk, Raya’s best friend and trusty steed; Lucille Soong as Dang Hu, the leader of the land of Talon; Patti Harrison as the chief of the Tail land; and Ross Butler as chief of the Spine land.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rayaandthelastdragon
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DisneyRaya
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/disneyraya/
Hashtag: #DisneyRaya

snippet.title: These Ponds Help Support Half The People On Earth
snippet.description:
What are these electric blue ponds in the middle of the Utah desert? And why do they keep changing color?

Join Derek Muller (Veritasium) as he looks into the weird, bizarre, and seemingly inexplicable images found on Google Earth to discover what on Earth they actually are. It’s a travel vlog, documentary, and science show wrapped into one. It’s Pindrop.

snippet.title: Story Teaser - Yakshas: The Guardian Adepti | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Alatus is the Golden-Winged King who is also the Conqueror of Demons. None knows whence he came, nor whither he went.
Only at springtime, during the offering of lanterns at night, might the people see the glow at Guyun and declare: "Behold, the Vigilant Yaksha ends the dominion of daemons!"
Or they might hear the sound of a flute amongst the marsh reeds, but find none who play the flute, and thus declare: "Hark, the yaksha calls to summon his old friends to their homeland."

localizations.es.description:
Alatus es conocido como el Rey de las Alas Doradas, también llamado el Gran Cazador de Demonios. Nadie sabe de dónde vino ni adónde fue.
Solo durante la noche primaveral del Rito de la Linterna, puede verse su resplandor en el Bosque de Piedra Guyun. Los habitantes de Liyue exclaman: "He aquí el Guardián Yaksha que terminará con el yugo de los demonios".
Le sigue el sonido sin autor de una flauta, proveniente del lejano Pantano Dihua. "¡Escuchen! Es el llamado del Yaksha invocando a sus viejos amigos".

localizations.fr.description:
Alatus, Roi aux Ailes d'Or, Dompteur de démons. De son origine comme de sa fin nul n'a connaissance.
Seulement lors de l'offrande des lanternes à la nuit de printemps, son éclat domine les pierres de Guyun. Alors le peuple dit :

localizations.de.title: Handlungsvorschau von Genshin Impact – „Yakshas, die schützenden Adepten“
localizations.de.description:
Alatus wird auch König mit den goldenen Flügeln oder großer Dämonenbändiger genannt. Niemand weiß, woher er eigentlich kam und wohin er eines Tages ging.
Nur im Frühling während der Nächte, in denen das Laternenritual gefeiert wird, bewundern die Bewohner von Liyue das Leuchten der Guyun-Türme und sagen, „Seht, unser Schützender Yaksha zaubert wieder!“.
Und nur dann konnten sie das Pfeifen aus dem Dihua-Moor hören und es für den Klang einer Flöte halten, dennoch keine solche finden und so erklärten sie: „Hört, der Yaksha ruft seine alten Freunde, um sie in die Heimat zu holen.“

Алатус, он же Златокрылый король, он же Укротитель демонов. Откуда пришёл он, куда ушёл - неведомо.
Лишь в весеннюю ночь, когда огни фонарей взлетают в небо, и люди Ли Юэ смотрят на их блеск над каменным лесом Гуюнь и говорят: «То защитники Яксы сражаются с демонами». 
А порой льётся среди болотных тростников тихий свист, но нет того, кто играл бы на флейте в тот час, и тогда говорят: «Это якса зовёт своих старых друзей домой».

localizations.vi.description:

snippet.title: LAKERS at 76ERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | January 27, 2021
snippet.description:
LAKERS at 76ERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | January 27, 2021

Tobias Harris knocked down a go-ahead basket with 2.4 seconds remaining in regulation to lift the Philadelphia 76ers over the Los Angeles Lakers, 107-106, handing the Lakers their first road loss of the season. Joel Embiid (28 PTS, 6 REB, 4 AST) and Tobias Harris (24 PTS, 7 REB) led the way for the 76ers, while Ben Simmons added 17 PTS, 11 REB and 10 AST in the victory, the 31st triple-double of his career. LeBron James tallied 34 PTS, 6 REB and 6 AST for the Lakers.

snippet.title: Perseverance Mars Rover Pre-Landing News Conference
snippet.description:
After nearly 300 million miles, our Perseverance rover completes its journey to Mars on Feb. 18, 2021. To reach the surface of the Red Planet, it has to survive the harrowing final phase known as Entry, Descent, and Landing.

On Jan. 27 at 4:30 p.m. EST, find out more about the upcoming landing from the scientists and engineers on the team: 

Thomas Zurbuchen, associate administrator, Science Mission Directorate, NASA Headquarters
Lori Glaze, director, Planetary Science Division, NASA Headquarters
Matt Wallace, Mars 2020 deputy project manager, JPL
Allen Chen, Mars 2020 entry, descent, and landing lead, JPL
Ken Farley, Mars 2020 project scientist, Caltech
Briony Horgan, Mars 2020 science team member, Purdue University

snippet.title: How to Repair a DEEP SCRATCH in Car Paint (DIY)
snippet.description:
Learn how to repair a deep scratch in the paint of your car. In this case someone keyed my car so I will show you how to remove a deep scratch from that using a touch up paint pen. Fixing scratches in your car's paint is simple and if they are just clear coat scratches it is even easier. 

To remove deep scratches you need to clean the scratch, sand the scratch, use touchup paint on the scratch, sand that paint smooth with the factory paint job, add clear coat, and wet sand that smooth with the factory paint. Then you can polish the whole panel and you are done!

Clear Coat Scratch Repair: https://youtu.be/2nYF46P7B2c

Paint Pen: https://advanceautoparts.rt8x.net/voOO3
1000-1500-2000 Grit:  https://advanceautoparts.rt8x.net/mD0b7
3000 Grit Sandpaper: https://advanceautoparts.rt8x.net/x0Rbx
5000 Grit Sandpaper: https://advanceautoparts.rt8x.net/QRWea
Polish: https://advanceautoparts.rt8x.net/rABbj
Polishing Pad: https://amzn.to/2YcLJEG
Microfiber Towel: http://amzn.to/1TQK01h

snippet.title: Danny MacAskill - The Slabs
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more: https://www.youtube.com/dannymacaskill?sub_confirmation=1

A Danny MacAskill film by Peny - https://www.wearepeny.com/  

With many of our overseas filming plans cancelled as a result of recent times myself and the crew decided to look a little closer to home for our latest film. 

I am a big fan of rock climbing and have been inspired by the various men and woman who set new routes and test themselves on some amazing faces around the world so I set out to find some challenging Slab Rock routes on my home Island of Skye with an aim to ride them in a continuous line and test what was possible on my bike. The remote Dubh Slabs rising out of Loch Coruisk in the heart of the Black Cuilin ridge provided some of the steepest terrain I have ever ridden as well as an amazing back drop for the film. 

The remote location and steep face forced us to think outside the box and meant we had to move away from traditional filming techniques, with us opting to shoot the entire film using GoPros mounted on myself and an FPV (First Person View) racing drone.

snippet.title: Welcome to The Arsenal, Martin Odegaard | First Interview
snippet.description:
Norwegian international Martin Odegaard is joining us from Real Madrid on loan for the remainder of the season.

Technical director Edu said: “We are delighted to welcome Martin to the club until the end of the season. I would like to thank everyone at Real Madrid and Martin’s representatives for their collaboration in making this loan move happen. Martin is an exceptional talent and we are strengthening our squad by introducing an exciting offensive player to the club for the remaining months of this season.” 

Mikel Arteta said: “It’s great that we’ve secured Martin to come to us until the end of the season. Martin is of course a player that we all know very well and although still young, he has been playing at the top level for a while. Martin will provide us with quality offensive options and we’re all excited to be integrating him into our plans between now and May.”

'It seems like a great project and a great club!'

The attacking midfielder started his career in Norway with Stromsgodset, where he made his debut as a 15-year-old in April 2014, becoming the youngest-ever player to feature in the top division. After featuring regularly in the Stromsgodset team in his first season, Odegaard was signed by Real Madrid in January 2015 and subsequently became their youngest player in May 2015. 

In the three seasons from 2017/18, Martin spent loan spells with Heerenveen and Vitesse Arnhem in the Netherlands and then last season back in Spain with Real Sociedad, where he helped the club reach the final of the Copa Del Rey and also qualify for the Europa League.

The 22-year-old has also made 25 appearances for Norway, making his debut in August 2014 when he became the youngest debutant for his country’s senior national team at the age of just 15 years and 253 days. 

Martin will wear the number 11 shirt.

Everyone at Arsenal welcomes Martin to the club.

The loan agreement is subject to the completion of legal and regulatory processes.

snippet.title: These Ponds Help Support Half The People On Earth
snippet.description:
What are these electric blue ponds in the middle of the Utah desert? And why do they keep changing color?

Join Derek Muller (Veritasium) as he looks into the weird, bizarre, and seemingly inexplicable images found on Google Earth to discover what on Earth they actually are. It’s a travel vlog, documentary, and science show wrapped into one. It’s Pindrop.

snippet.title: Apex Legends Season 8 – Mayhem Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Bring the boom in Apex Legends Season 8 with new Legend Fuse.  http://x.ea.com/67416

Fuse arrives in Season 8, and he’s packing plenty of attitude -- and things that go boom. Pick apart the opposition with the Salvo’s most popular weapon, the lever-action 30-30 Repeater. Explore an obliterated Kings Canyon reshaped by Fuse’s arrival. Look out for Gold Magazines, capable of automatically reloading holstered weapons. Plus grab the latest Battle Pass and blast through the competition in Ranked. Ready to master the mayhem?

暴雷将在第 8 赛季登场，而且诚意满满——当然还有一堆会爆炸的东西。拿好萨尔沃最流行的武器：杠杆式“30-30 连发枪”，将敌人撕成碎片。探索因暴雷的到来而地形变样的疮痍诸王峡谷，留意寻找黄金弹匣，能够自动给收起的武器重新装弹。再入手最新的战斗通行证，在排位赛中炸出一条血路。准备好在死斗中掌控战场了吗？

localizations.ru.description:
Устройте большой бум в сезоне 8 Apex Legends с новой легендой Фьюзом: http://x.ea.com/67416

В сезоне 8 в игру прибывает Фьюз, знаменитый своим гонором — и любовью к взрывам. Разберитесь с врагами с помощью любимого оружия Сальво — рычажной магазинной винтовки 30-30. Исследуйте Каньон Кингс, разрушенный в ходе прибытия Фьюза. Ищите золотые магазины, которые автоматически перезаряжают убранное оружие. И не забудьте прихватить новый боевой пропуск и разорвать врагов в рейтинговых боях. Готовы ли вы устроить переполох?

localizations.ar.description:
"اجلب الأمور الرائعة في Apex Legends Season 8 مع الأسطورة الجديدة Fuse.  http://x.ea.com/67416

يصل Fuse إلى الموسم 8, وهو يحمل العديد من السلوكيات السيئة, بالإضافة إلى أشياء رائعة. دمّر المعارضة مع السلاح الأشهر في Salvo, بندقية ‎30-30 Repeater اليدوية. استكشف Kings Canyon المدمّر الذي تغيّر بوصول Fuse. ابحث عن الخزانات الذهبية, القادرة على إعادة تعبئة الأسلحة الموضوعة في حافظاتها بصورة تلقائية. بالإضافة إلى ذلك, احصل على أحدث Battle Pass وانطلق بقوة عبر المنافسة في Ranked. هل أنت مستعد لإتقان الفوضى العارمة؟

Apex Legends™‎ هي لعبة معارك مجانية حيث تتقاتل شخصيات أسطورية بحثًا عن المجد والشهرة والثروة على أطراف Frontier. العب بالمجان الآن على PlayStation® 4, وPlayStation 5, وXbox One, وXbox Series X|S, والكمبيوتر الشخصي من خلال Origin وSteam.  
تعرّف على المزيد عن Apex Legends Season 8 – Mayhem الذي سيتوفر في 2 فبراير: http://x.ea.com/67416

localizations.fi.title: Apex Legends Season 8 – Mayhemin Gameplay-traileri
localizations.fi.description:
Laita aseet laulamaan Apex Legends Season 8:ssa uudella Legendalla nimeltään Fuse. http://x.ea.com/67416

Fuse saapuu Season 8:lla, ja hän on täynnä asennetta – räjähtävää sellaista. Tee vihollisista muusia Salvon suosituimmalla aseella, vipulukkoisella 30-30 Repeaterilla. Tutki tuhoutunutta Kings Canyonia, jota Fusen saapuminen on muokannut raskaalla kädellä. Etsi kultaisia lippaita, jotka lataavat kotelossa olevat aseet automaattisesti. Ja nappaa uusin Battle Pass ja tee kilpailijoista selvää Ranked-pelissä. Oletko valmis näyttämään kyntesi?

Apex Legends™ on ilmainen battle royale -peli, jossa legendaariset hahmot taistelevat maineesta, kunniasta ja mammonasta Frontierin laitamilla. Pelaa nyt ilmaiseksi seuraavilla alustoilla: PlayStation® 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S ja PC (Origin tai Steam).

localizations.no.title: Apex Legends – sesong 8: Mayhem – spilltrailer
localizations.no.description:
La det smelle i Apex Legends™ – sesong 8 med den nye legenden Fuse. http://x.ea.com/67416

Fuse inntar lekene i sesong 8 med skikkelig stil – samt en del ting som kan eksplodere. Demonter motstanden med Salvos mest populære våpen, en 30-30 Repeater med bøylemekanisme. Utforsk et ødelagt Kings Canyon, omformet av Fuses ankomst. Vær på utkikk etter gullmagasiner, som automatisk lader om våpnene i hylsteret. Skaff deg spillets nyeste Battle Pass og spreng deg til topps i Ranked. Klar til å mestre kaoset?

Apex Legends™ er et gratis battle royale-spill hvor legendariske karakterer kjemper om rikdom og ære i ved Frontiers utkant. Spill gratis nå på PlayStation®4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, og PC via Origin og Steam.

Start med et brag i Apex Legends sæson 8 med den nye legende Fuse.  http://x.ea.com/67416

Fuse ankommer i sæson 8, og han ankommer med stil – og et par ting, der kan sige bom. Split modstanderne til atomer med Salvos mest populære våben: bøjlespænderen 30-30 Repeater. Tänd stubinen i Apex Legends Säsong 8 med den nya legendaren Fuse. http://x.ea.com/67416

Fuse gör entré i säsong 8 med en hel del attityd – och massor av sprängämnen. Krossa allt motstånd med Salvos populäraste vapen: 30-30 Repeater. localizations.nl-NL.title: Apex Legends Season 8 – Gameplay-trailer Mayhem
localizations.nl-NL.description:
Laat het knallen in Apex Legends Season 8 met de nieuwe Legend Fuse. http://x.ea.com/67416

Fuse komt aan in Season 8, en hij loopt over van zelfvertrouwen -- en dingen die knallen. Rijt de tegenstander uiteen met het populairste wapen van Salvo: de 30-30 Repeater met grendelactie. Verken een verwoest Kings Canyon dat een nieuwe vorm heeft gekregen na de komst van Fuse. Kijk uit naar Gold Magazines, die geholsterde wapens automatisch kunnen herladen. Ontvang daarnaast de nieuwste Battle Pass en baan je knallend een weg door de concurrentie in Ranked. Ben jij klaar om over de chaos te heersen?

Apex Legends™ is een free-to-play battle royale-spel waarin legendarische personages strijden om glorie, roem en fortuin aan de rand van de Frontier. Speel nu gratis op de PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S en pc via Origin en Steam.

localizations.es-ES.title: Tráiler de la mecánica de juego de la temporada 8 de Apex Legends: Estragos
localizations.es-ES.description:
Hora de explotarlo todo en la temporada 8 de Apex Legends con Fuse, la nueva leyenda.  http://x.ea.com/67416

Fuse llega en la temporada 8 con muchas ganas y un montón de cosas que explotan. Derrota a tus oponentes con el arma más popular de Salvo, el rifle de palanca 30-30 Repeater. Explora un Cañón de los Reyes destruido, que ha cambiado con la llegada de Fuse. Busca los cargadores de oro, que recargan automáticamente las armas enfundadas. Además, consigue el último pase de batalla y aniquila a los rivales en los Rangos de clasificación. ¿Todo listo para dominar el caos?

Apex Legends™ es un juego de Battle Royale gratuito donde personajes legendarios se enfrentan para lograr gloria, fama y fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega gratis ya en PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S y PC a través de Origin y Steam.

snippet.title: 16-year-old detained under Singapore's Internal Security Act after planning to attack two mosques
snippet.description:
A 16-year-old has been detained under Singapore's Internal Security Act. He had planned to attack Muslims at two local mosques on the second anniversary of the Christchurch attacks on March 15. The authorities said the secondary school student is the youngest to be detained under the act, and the first to be inspired by far-right extremist ideology. The youth is a Protestant Christian of Indian ethnicity. He had planned to attack Muslims at Assyafaah Mosque and Yusof Ishak Mosque. The mosques are about 4km apart and located near his home.

snippet.title: Godzilla vs. Kong – Official Trailer
snippet.description:
In theaters and streaming exclusively on @HBOMax* March 26.
 
*Available on @HBOMax in the US only, for 31 days, at no extra cost to subscribers.

https://www.godzillavskong.com/
https://www.facebook.com/GodzillaVsKong
https://www.instagram.com/godzillavskong/
https://twitter.com/GodzillaVsKong

---

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures comes the long-awaited face-off between two icons, “Godzilla vs. Kong,” the next epic adventure in Legendary’s cinematic Monsterverse, directed by Adam Wingard.

Legends collide in “Godzilla vs. Kong” as these mythic adversaries meet in a spectacular battle for the ages, with the fate of the world hanging in the balance.  Kong and his protectors undertake a perilous journey to find his true home, and with them is Jia, a young orphaned girl with whom he has formed a unique and powerful bond.  But they unexpectedly find themselves in the path of an enraged Godzilla, cutting a swath of destruction across the globe.  The epic clash between the two titans—instigated by unseen forces—is only the beginning of the mystery that lies deep within the core of the Earth.

The film stars Alexander Skarsgård (“Big Little Lies,” “The Little Drummer Girl”), Millie Bobby Brown (“Stranger Things”), Rebecca Hall (“Christine,” “Professor Marston and the Wonder Women”), Brian Tyree Henry (“Joker,” “Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse”), Shun Oguri (“Weathering with You”), Eiza González (“Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw”), Julian Dennison (“Deadpool 2”), with Kyle Chandler (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”) and Demián Bichir (“The Nun,” “The Hateful Eight”).
Wingard (“The Guest,” “You’re Next”) directed from a screenplay by Eric Pearson (“Thor: Ragnarok”) and Max Borenstein (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters,” “Kong: Skull Island”), story by Terry Rossio (“Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales”) and Michael Dougherty & Zach Shields (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”), based on the character “Godzilla” owned and created by TOHO CO., LTD.  The film was produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric McLeod, Jon Jashni, Thomas Tull and Brian Rogers, with Jay Ashenfelter, Herbert W. Gains, Dan Lin, Roy Lee, Yoshimitsu Banno and Kenji Okuhira executive producing.

The director’s behind-the-scenes creative team included director of photography Ben Seresin (“The Mummy,” “World War Z”), production designers Owen Paterson (“Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle,” “Godzilla”) and Thomas S. Hammock (“Blair Witch”), editor Josh Schaeffer (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”), costume designer Ann Foley (“Skyscraper”) and visual effects supervisor John “DJ” DesJardin (upcoming “Zack Snyder’s Justice League”).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, “Godzilla vs. Kong.”  The film will be released nationwide in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX on March 26, 2021 and will be available in the U.S. on HBO Max for 31 days from theatrical release.  It is rated PG-13 for intense sequences of creature violence/destruction and brief language.

《乘风破浪的姐姐》是芒果TV推出的女团成长综艺节目，与其他女团选秀不同，该节目召集了30位1990年之前出生的女艺人，并最终选出7位成员组成女团。在第二季节目中，大众评审按照年龄分为30+和30-两大阵营。赛制上也变得更加残酷，初舞台表演要有Vocal（唱）和Dance（跳）两项，两项分开表演且缺一不可。节目焦点从女性的精彩绽放渗透到她们成功背后付出的努力和奋斗，表现出丰富多样化的女性价值观，诠释自信奋斗的“她力量”，让更多女性能从中感受到自我价值的体现。

《乘風破浪的姐姐》是芒果TV推出的女團成長綜藝節目，與其他女團選秀不同，該節目召集了30位1990年之前出生的女藝人，並最終選出7位成員組成女團。在第二季節目中，大眾評審按照年齡分為30+和30-兩大陣營。賽制上也變得更加殘酷，初舞臺表演要有Vocal（唱）和Dance（跳）兩項，兩項分開表演且缺一不可。節目焦點從女性的精彩綻放滲透到她們成功背後付出的努力和奮鬥，表現出豐富多樣化的女性價值觀，詮釋自信奮鬥的“她力量”，讓更多女性能從中感受到自我價值的體現。

snippet.title: WATCH LIVE: The presidential inauguration of Joe Biden and Kamala Harris — 1/20/21
snippet.description:
Joe Biden is set to become the nation’s 46th president today. He is slated to take the oath of office around noon, which is when Donald Trump’s term as president ends. Sign up for CNBC Pro to stream the inauguration with commentary: http://cnb.cx/3iC88Vl

Set against a backdrop of a locked-down Washington, D.C., and a socially distanced ceremony, Biden, in his inaugural address, is expected to plead for national unity as political, economic and health care crises grip the nation. He will take over the presidency two weeks after a deadly pro-Trump riot at Capitol Hill and as deaths from Covid-19 continue to surge. Since the pandemic began early last year, the disease has killed more than 400,000 people in the United States.

Kamala Harris will make history as the country’s first Black, female and South Asian vice president.

The first members of Biden’s Cabinet are slated to be sworn in over the next few days, as well, including Janet Yellen as Treasury secretary. Biden’s Democratic Party, likewise, will assume a bare majority in the Senate after three new lawmakers – Raphael Warnock and Jon Ossoff of Georgia, and Alex Padilla of California – also take their oaths of office.

snippet.title: Is Godzilla The Bad Guy In Godzilla vs. Kong?
snippet.description:
We've finally got our first real look at Godzilla vs. Kong and while there's certainly a lot to unpack in this trailer, perhaps the biggest question is: what's the deal with Godzilla and why is he being such a jerk?

The epic next chapter in the cinematic Monsterverse pits two of the greatest icons in motion picture history against one another - the fearsome Godzilla and the mighty Kong - with humanity caught in the balance. 

Godzilla Vs. Kong comes to cinemas and HBO Max in 2021 and stars Alexander Skarsgård, Millie Bobby Brown and Rebecca Hall. Godzilla Vs. Kong is directed by Adam Wingard (Blair Witch, Death Note) and is the latest film is Warner Bros Monsterverse, following on from Gareth Edwards' Godzilla, Kong: Skull Island  and Godzilla: King of the Monsters.  
   
In a time when monsters walk the Earth, humanity’s fight for its future sets Godzilla and Kong on a collision course that will see the two most powerful forces of nature on the planet collide in a spectacular battle for the ages. As Monarch embarks on a perilous mission into uncharted terrain and unearths clues to the Titans’ origins, a human conspiracy threatens to wipe the creatures, both good and bad, from the face of the earth forever.

snippet.title: WATCH: Harris escorts the Pences as they depart U.S. Capitol
snippet.description:
Skip to 12:49 to watch Harris and Emhoff escort the Pences down the Capitol steps.

Vice President Kamala Harris and second gentleman Douglas Emhoff escorted former Vice President Mike Pence and second lady Karen Pence to their departure from the U.S. Capitol after Harris and President Joe Biden were sworn in on Wednesday.

While former President Donald Trump never formally conceded to Biden, Pence called Harris to offer his congratulations and assistance in the transition five days ago.

snippet.localized.description:
Skip to 12:49 to watch Harris and Emhoff escort the Pences down the Capitol steps.

Vice President Kamala Harris and second gentleman Douglas Emhoff escorted former Vice President Mike Pence and second lady Karen Pence to their departure from the U.S. Capitol after Harris and President Joe Biden were sworn in on Wednesday.

While former President Donald Trump never formally conceded to Biden, Pence called Harris to offer his congratulations and assistance in the transition five days ago.

snippet.title: Godzilla vs. Kong – Official Trailer
snippet.description:
In theaters and streaming exclusively on @HBOMax* March 26.
 
*Available on @HBOMax in the US only, for 31 days, at no extra cost to subscribers.

https://www.godzillavskong.com/
https://www.facebook.com/GodzillaVsKong
https://www.instagram.com/godzillavskong/
https://twitter.com/GodzillaVsKong

---

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures comes the long-awaited face-off between two icons, “Godzilla vs. Kong,” the next epic adventure in Legendary’s cinematic Monsterverse, directed by Adam Wingard.

Legends collide in “Godzilla vs. Kong” as these mythic adversaries meet in a spectacular battle for the ages, with the fate of the world hanging in the balance.  Kong and his protectors undertake a perilous journey to find his true home, and with them is Jia, a young orphaned girl with whom he has formed a unique and powerful bond.  But they unexpectedly find themselves in the path of an enraged Godzilla, cutting a swath of destruction across the globe.  The epic clash between the two titans—instigated by unseen forces—is only the beginning of the mystery that lies deep within the core of the Earth.

The film stars Alexander Skarsgård (“Big Little Lies,” “The Little Drummer Girl”), Millie Bobby Brown (“Stranger Things”), Rebecca Hall (“Christine,” “Professor Marston and the Wonder Women”), Brian Tyree Henry (“Joker,” “Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse”), Shun Oguri (“Weathering with You”), Eiza González (“Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw”), Julian Dennison (“Deadpool 2”), with Kyle Chandler (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”) and Demián Bichir (“The Nun,” “The Hateful Eight”).
Wingard (“The Guest,” “You’re Next”) directed from a screenplay by Eric Pearson (“Thor: Ragnarok”) and Max Borenstein (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters,” “Kong: Skull Island”), story by Terry Rossio (“Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales”) and Michael Dougherty & Zach Shields (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”), based on the character “Godzilla” owned and created by TOHO CO., LTD.  The film was produced by Mary Parent, Alex Garcia, Eric McLeod, Jon Jashni, Thomas Tull and Brian Rogers, with Jay Ashenfelter, Herbert W. Gains, Dan Lin, Roy Lee, Yoshimitsu Banno and Kenji Okuhira executive producing.

The director’s behind-the-scenes creative team included director of photography Ben Seresin (“The Mummy,” “World War Z”), production designers Owen Paterson (“Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle,” “Godzilla”) and Thomas S. Hammock (“Blair Witch”), editor Josh Schaeffer (“Godzilla: King of the Monsters”), costume designer Ann Foley (“Skyscraper”) and visual effects supervisor John “DJ” DesJardin (upcoming “Zack Snyder’s Justice League”).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present a Legendary Pictures Production, A Film By Adam Wingard, “Godzilla vs. Kong.”  The film will be released nationwide in 2D and 3D in select theaters and IMAX on March 26, 2021 and will be available in the U.S. on HBO Max for 31 days from theatrical release.  It is rated PG-13 for intense sequences of creature violence/destruction and brief language.

snippet.title: Documenting America's Underbelly - ALL GAS NO BRAKES
snippet.description:
Andrew Callaghan's series ALL GAS NO BRAKES captures the underbelly of American culture as he crisscrosses the country in a rusty RV.  Interviewing people on the fringes of society, the success of the show has made Andrew's oversized suit and bushy hair famous. In this episode of My Life Online, we meet up with Andrew and his crew in Sturgis, South Dakota for the annual motorcycle rally that is taking place during the COVID-19 pandemic to see how the sausage gets made.

snippet.title: WATCH LIVE: The presidential inauguration of Joe Biden and Kamala Harris — 1/20/21
snippet.description:
Joe Biden is set to become the nation’s 46th president today. He is slated to take the oath of office around noon, which is when Donald Trump’s term as president ends. Sign up for CNBC Pro to stream the inauguration with commentary: http://cnb.cx/3iC88Vl

Set against a backdrop of a locked-down Washington, D.C., and a socially distanced ceremony, Biden, in his inaugural address, is expected to plead for national unity as political, economic and health care crises grip the nation. He will take over the presidency two weeks after a deadly pro-Trump riot at Capitol Hill and as deaths from Covid-19 continue to surge. Since the pandemic began early last year, the disease has killed more than 400,000 people in the United States.

Kamala Harris will make history as the country’s first Black, female and South Asian vice president.

The first members of Biden’s Cabinet are slated to be sworn in over the next few days, as well, including Janet Yellen as Treasury secretary. Biden’s Democratic Party, likewise, will assume a bare majority in the Senate after three new lawmakers – Raphael Warnock and Jon Ossoff of Georgia, and Alex Padilla of California – also take their oaths of office.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Southampton vs Arsenal (1-3) | Pepe, Saka & Lacazette fire us to victory
snippet.description:
We came from behind to claim all three points on the road and make it six games without defeat in the Premier League.

The forward line was in excellent form all evening with Nicolas Pepe, Bukayo Saka and Alexandre Lacazette all on target as we gained swift revenge for the weekend's FA Cup defeat here at St Mary's.

The Saints needed just three minutes to open the scoring, but we should have been ahead even before that. Granit Xhaka released Lacazette into the box, but the Frenchman's low shot was saved by the legs of Alex McCarthy as he bore down on goal.

The miss was compounded when the hosts went ahead through a thumping Stuart Armstrong volley from James Ward-Prowse's out-swinging corner.

We maintained our intensity though and got on terms through Pepe, who kept his cool inside the box to slide the ball into the corner after being set up by Xhaka.

Chances kept coming and it was certainly a more entertaining match than the FA Cup game here just three days ago, with Pepe and Saka seeing plenty of the ball on the wings.

The game eventually settled down, though it remained entertaining with both sides pushing men forward.

We went into the break in the lead thanks to a wonderful goal from Saka. Lacazette fed the youngster with a perfectly weighted pass, and the England man did the rest – skipping past McCarthy and then calmly rolled the ball home right footed from outside the box. It was his fourth goal in his last six league starts - he is certainly enjoying life on the right wing.

It was a much more measured start to the second half. The game was on a knife edge as the hosts began to peg us back.

But our third goal killed their impetus. The impressive Cedric found Saka on the opposite flank, and his low cross was converted from close range by Lacazette.

Bernd Leno made a superb save from a Ward-Prowse free-kick late on and Rob Holding tackled Che Adams in the area as Southampton made us work until the last minute for the three points that lift us to eighth.

snippet.description:
Dustin Poirier stopped Conor McGregor with a flurry of punches midway through the second round on Sunday, avenging his loss to the Irish superstar with a knockout victory at UFC 257. Poirier caught McGregor with a series of shots to the head before sending him to to the canvas with a short right hand, setting off stunned excitement among the few thousand screaming fans allowed inside the Etihad Arena on Yas Island.

snippet.title: We Spoke to a Lone Trump Supporter at Biden's Inauguration
snippet.description:
With heightened security and pandemic precautions, the streets of Washington, DC were mostly empty on the day of Joe Biden’s inauguration. Despite vowing to once again storm the Capitol, Trump supporters were nowhere to be seen. We spoke to one man in a MAGA hat who traveled from New York for a rally that never happened.

snippet.description:

Learn EXACTLY how to get your first 1000 subscribers on YouTube, rank videos on the front page of searches, grow your following, and turn that into another income source: https://bit.ly/2STxofv $100 OFF WITH CODE 100OFF 

My ENTIRE Camera and Recording Equipment: 
https://www.amazon.com/shop/grahamstephan?listId=2TNWZ7RP1P1EB

Like the name would suggest, this was a retail gaming shop that sold video games, consoles, controllers, and collectables. But, as the overall video-game market began outgrowing the store, and more and more people shifted towards online downloads versus shopping in outdated malls with nothing left. 

In June of 2020, GameStop announced that they saw a 519% jump in online sales when they were forced to shut down their physical locations. 

In August of 2020, The Billionaire Co-Founder of Chewy.com, announces that he bought a 9% stake in the company, and plans to turn it into an Amazon Rival through his active involvement and re-management of the company. 

After that, they announced a multi-year strategic partnership with Microsoft, with plans to expand both their physical store - AND, their digital store. 

Sure enough, digital sales increased - and the Chewy.com co-founder increased his stake in GameStop to now 13%. 

And that’s when, about 4 months ago…users on WallStreetBets discovered a little-known secret of the stock that would cause it to skyrocket exponentially, just given the right conditions….and, sure enough, he was right, and EVERYTHING he said 4 months ago is coming true… 

He explained that GameStop was one of the most SHORTED stocks on the market, with almost 90% of stockholders betting the price will GO DOWN. In fact, it was SO SHORTED, that MORE SHARES WERE SHORTED than actually exist in the market for sale…so, that’s turning out to be the perfect storm to cause this price to SKYROCKET as soon as there’s ANY GOOD news.

This user theorized that - because SO many people were short on GameStop - EVENTUALLY, all this good news is going to cause those short sellers to EXIT their positions, causing them to BUY BACK those shares at higher prices, and when that happens - the price of the stock goes up, and when THAT happens - MORE people close out their positions by buying back shares at a higher price - and that continues until the price of GameStop goes to the moon.

Now, as for where this goes from here…it’s anyone’s guess. At this point, it has NOTHING to do with the fundamentals of the company AT ALL…BUT, it has to do with a unique situation of a limited quantity of shares available, combined with short seller interest, combined with WallStreetBets, which causes more people to pile in…and it’s a perfect storm, when those people refuse to sell what they’ve just bought. 

This is probably one of the riskiest, most speculative bets I’ve ever talked about here on the channel…so, as my word of caution here: DON’T DO IT. 

More importantly, though - this DOES represent a BIG SHIFT of power away from large, corporate institutional investors…and into the hands of retail traders, or groups like WallStreetBets. I honestly think the power of retail traders have been GROSSLY underestimated for quite some time, and THIS is a good example that WallStreetBets should NOT be taken lightly. NOT INVESTMENT ADVICE.

snippet.title: Prime Time With Ravish Kumar: Police की खुफिया नाकामी या किसानों के आगे पुलिस कम पड़ गई?
snippet.description:
Prime Time With Ravish Kumar - January 26, 2021: असफलता किसकी थी इस मुद्दे पर बहस लंबी हो जाएगी. और जवाबदेही भी कभी तय नहीं हो पाएगी. तीन-तीन राज्यों की पुलिस हालात को संभाल नहीं पायी. और संयुक्त किसान मोर्चा के नेता भी अपने घटक के संगठनों को नहीं संभाल पाए. कई दिनों से पुलिस के अधिकारियों की किसान नेताओं के साथ बैठक चल रही थी कुछ तो अंदाजा होगा कि इतनी बड़ी संख्या में किसान आ रहे हैं. कुछ लोग रास्ते से भटक सकते हैं.ऐसे में पुलिस की तैयारी क्या होनी चाहिए? आज जिस तरह से लाल किले (Red Fort) तक किसान पहुंचे ऐसे में लगता नहीं है कि पुलिस के पास कोई बैकअप प्लान था.

localizations.hi.description:
Prime Time With Ravish Kumar - January 26, 2021: असफलता किसकी थी इस मुद्दे पर बहस लंबी हो जाएगी. और जवाबदेही भी कभी तय नहीं हो पाएगी. तीन-तीन राज्यों की पुलिस हालात को संभाल नहीं पायी. और संयुक्त किसान मोर्चा के नेता भी अपने घटक के संगठनों को नहीं संभाल पाए. कई दिनों से पुलिस के अधिकारियों की किसान नेताओं के साथ बैठक चल रही थी कुछ तो अंदाजा होगा कि इतनी बड़ी संख्या में किसान आ रहे हैं. कुछ लोग रास्ते से भटक सकते हैं.ऐसे में पुलिस की तैयारी क्या होनी चाहिए? आज जिस तरह से लाल किले (Red Fort) तक किसान पहुंचे ऐसे में लगता नहीं है कि पुलिस के पास कोई बैकअप प्लान था.

snippet.title: PALMEIRAS 1x1 VASCO; GALO 2x0 SANTOS; DINIZ x CENI; MELHOR GRINGO do BRASIL? | De Placa (27/01/21)
snippet.description:
No #DePlaca de hoje vamos falar sobre os jogos atrasados do Brasileirão. Trabalho rápido e certeiro de Abel Ferreira e Cuca devem ser exemplos no Brasil? Vamos fazer também um jogo dos cenários entre Fernando Diniz e Rogério Ceni. Além disso, aproveitando o gancho dos dois gols de Savarino na partida contra o Peixe, a galera da produção preparou uma estafeta para saber qual é o melhor gringo do futebol brasileiro na temporada. Isso e muito mais. Vem com a gente!

Se inscreva no canal para não perder nenhum De Placa! De segunda a sexta, 10h30, com o melhor debate esportivo do Youtube!

Em apenas três anos, MIDIAN LIMA se tornou um dos maiores nomes da música cristã do país e tem construído uma surpreendente e consistente história musical. Com mais de 500 milhões de views no YouTube só nos últimos 12 meses, a cantora é um dos artistas brasileiros mais assistidos na plataforma! O seu primeiro hit, “Jó”, deu início à sua linda trajetória – o clipe oficial ultrapassou 390 milhões de visualizações no YouTube e viralizou nas plataformas digitais (são mais de 24 milhões de plays no Spotify). Mas sua linda e emocionante história de vida está registrada agora em single e videoclipe “Sou Teu Deus”. 

“Eu recebi esta canção em um momento muito especial, em que estava em missão fora do Brasil e tinha que decidir em continuar a viagem ou voltar para casa... Quando ouvi e meditei na letra, meu coração se encheu de paz e confiança nesse Deus maravilhoso. E esta mensagem é linda demais. Claro que eu tinha que gravar esta música e compartilhar com todo mundo esta palavra de força, para nunca nos esquecermos quem é o Senhor da nossa vida, a quem servimos...”, compartilha a cantora. 

“Minha cunhada, missionária Raquel, falou que eu precisava contar a minha história e compartilhar com todo mundo o que Deus fez na minha vida, cada livramento... Porque muitos podem estar me conhecendo hoje, recentemente, mas não sabe o que vivi e porque amo tanto esse Deus. E quando eu vi pela primeira chorei muito e não paro de me emocionar toda vez que vejo, porque é Deus operou e ainda opera milagres em minha vida”, completa.   

=============================================

snippet.title: Luma Elpidio - Liberta-me de mim  (Dançando com o Espírito)
snippet.description:
Ouça " Liberta-me de Mim (Versão Cinemática)" em todas as plataformas digitais: http://sl.onerpm.com/libertamedemim

--
REDES SOCIAIS OFICIAIS DA LUMA ELPIDIO:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lumaelpidio/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lumaelpidioo...
www.lumaelpidio.com

REDES SOCIAIS OFICIAIS DA LE MUSIC:
http://www.instagram.com/lemusic/
http://www.facebook.com/lemusicoficial/

--
Dirigido por João Frazão (@joaofrazao_)
Produção Geral: Le Music (@lemusic)
Direção Artística: Luma Elpidio (@lumaelpidio)
Edição e Finalização: João Frazão  (@frazaofilmes)

--
Produção Musical: Agner Magalhães (@agnermagalhaes)
Mixagem e Masterização: Dan Mezadri (@danmezadri)
Dançarino: Tyler Williams 
Letra e Música: Luma Elpidio (@lumaelpidio) 


_
LETRA:

Não entendo o meu próprio agir
Sem Tua graça o que seria de mim, Deus?

Pois o bem que eu quero fazer não faço
E o mal que eu não quero, esse sim
Acabo cometendo

Em meu ser militam Carne e Espírito
Em uma guerra infindável à qual
Eu não me rendo

Pois meu corpo já foi vendido como escravo
E não existe bem nenhum em mim
Apenas o pecado

Mas, eu sei, que no tocante ao meu interior
Tenho prazer na Sua lei
Tu és o meu amado

Então liberta-me de mim
Eu quero ser a Sua casa
Se Você estiver aqui
Eu sei, eu venço o pecado

Então enche-me de Ti
Até que não haja mais espaço
Pois quando estou em Tua presença
O meu viver é transformado

E eu passo a ser livre pra viver
A tua vontade boa, perfeita e agradável 

Ao te conhecer todo o meu ser 
Se enche de bondade

E reina o Espírito sobre a carne 
- 

#LumaElpidio #LibertaMeDeMim #LeMusic

snippet.title: Story Teaser - Yakshas: The Guardian Adepti | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Alatus is the Golden-Winged King who is also the Conqueror of Demons. None knows whence he came, nor whither he went.
Only at springtime, during the offering of lanterns at night, might the people see the glow at Guyun and declare: "Behold, the Vigilant Yaksha ends the dominion of daemons!"
Or they might hear the sound of a flute amongst the marsh reeds, but find none who play the flute, and thus declare: "Hark, the yaksha calls to summon his old friends to their homeland."

localizations.es.title: Avance de la trama de Genshin Impact: Yakshas, los guardianes Adeptus
localizations.es.description:
Alatus es conocido como el Rey de las Alas Doradas, también llamado el Gran Cazador de Demonios. Nadie sabe de dónde vino ni adónde fue.
Solo durante la noche primaveral del Rito de la Linterna, puede verse su resplandor en el Bosque de Piedra Guyun. Los habitantes de Liyue exclaman: "He aquí el Guardián Yaksha que terminará con el yugo de los demonios".
Le sigue el sonido sin autor de una flauta, proveniente del lejano Pantano Dihua. "¡Escuchen! Es el llamado del Yaksha invocando a sus viejos amigos".

localizations.fr.title: Genshin Impact - Aperçu de l'histoire : « Les Yakshas, gardiens Adeptes »
localizations.fr.description:
Alatus, Roi aux Ailes d'Or, Dompteur de démons. De son origine comme de sa fin nul n'a connaissance.
Seulement lors de l'offrande des lanternes à la nuit de printemps, son éclat domine les pierres de Guyun. Alors le peuple dit :
 « Oyez, le Gardien Yaksha terrasse les démons ».
Alors des marais retentit la flûte, mais nul n'est vu en jouer. Et le peuple dit : « Ses frères le Yaksha appelle. »

localizations.de.title: Handlungsvorschau von Genshin Impact – „Yakshas, die schützenden Adepten“
localizations.de.description:
Alatus wird auch König mit den goldenen Flügeln oder großer Dämonenbändiger genannt. Niemand weiß, woher er eigentlich kam und wohin er eines Tages ging.
Nur im Frühling während der Nächte, in denen das Laternenritual gefeiert wird, bewundern die Bewohner von Liyue das Leuchten der Guyun-Türme und sagen, „Seht, unser Schützender Yaksha zaubert wieder!“.
Und nur dann konnten sie das Pfeifen aus dem Dihua-Moor hören und es für den Klang einer Flöte halten, dennoch keine solche finden und so erklärten sie: „Hört, der Yaksha ruft seine alten Freunde, um sie in die Heimat zu holen.“

localizations.ru.title: Тизер «Якса: Защитники Адептов» | Genshin Impact
localizations.ru.description:
Алатус, он же Златокрылый король, он же Укротитель демонов. Откуда пришёл он, куда ушёл - неведомо.
Лишь в весеннюю ночь, когда огни фонарей взлетают в небо, и люди Ли Юэ смотрят на их блеск над каменным лесом Гуюнь и говорят: «То защитники Яксы сражаются с демонами». 
А порой льётся среди болотных тростников тихий свист, но нет того, кто играл бы на флейте в тот час, и тогда говорят: «Это якса зовёт своих старых друзей домой».

localizations.id.description:
Alatus — Raja Bersayap Emas yang juga dijuluki Conqueror of Demons. Tidak ada yang mengetahui asal-usulnya, dan juga tidak ada yang mengetahui tujuan akhirnya.
Hanya pada malam musim semi, saat lentera-lentera diterbangkan, penduduk Liyue yang melihat ke arah Guyun akan berseru: "Lihat, Vigilant Yaksha sedang memburu para iblis!"
Atau mereka akan mendengar suara seruling dari rawa-rawa, tetapi saat dicari, tidak ada seorang pun di sana. Mereka pun akan berseru: "Para Yaksha sedang memanggil rekan-rekan lamanya kembali ke kampung halaman mereka."

localizations.vi.title: Cốt Truyện Genshin Impact - Hộ Pháp Tiên Chúng Dạ Xoa
localizations.vi.description:
Kim Bằng tên hiệu là "Kim Sí Bằng Vương", còn có tên là "Hàng Ma Đại Thánh". Không rõ đến từ nơi nào, cũng không biết đi về đâu.
Chỉ vào dịp Tết Hải Đăng, khi thấy ánh sáng lơ lửng phía trên Cô Vân Các, người dân Liyue thường nói rằng: "Vị Dạ Xoa này đang chiến đấu với yêu quái."
Hoặc lúc nghe được tiếng sáo từ Địch Hoa Châu, đi tìm nhưng chẳng gặp người thổi sáo, sẽ nói rằng: "Là Dạ Xoa gọi bạn cũ quay về chăng."

localizations.pt.title: Teaser de Genshin Imapct - Yakshas: Os Guardiões Adepti
localizations.pt.description:
Alatus, vem de Alatus Nemeseos, conhecido como Conquistador de Demônios. Ambos sua origem e destino são um mistério.
Em uma noite completamente iluminada pelas Lanternas Celestes, uma figura ficou olhando para as nuvens na Floresta de Pedra Guyun, solitário e pensativo. Os habitantes de Liyue: "O Guardião Yaksha veio caçar os monstros de novo".
Seguindo o som da flauta, oriundo da Ilhota de Dihua, não consegui encontrá-lo, e aposto que esse Yaksha está chamando os seus velhos amigos de volta.

snippet.description:
Esse é o clipe oficial da faixa "Salva Vidas" que faz parte do álbum "Aquário".

Disponível em todos os apps de música: https://SomLivre.lnk.to/Aquario

Letra
Composição: SPVIC / Pedro Qualy / Spinardi / André Nine / Nox / Lotto

Fogo em pleno alto-mar
De noite ao amanhecer
Eu vim pra desconstruir
A multidão se sente só
Fogo em pleno alto-mar
De noite ao amanhecer
Eu vim pra desconstruir
A multidão se sente só, uh
Ah, de noite ao amanhecer
Eu vim pra desconstruir
A multidão se sente só, uh

Ahn, ahn
Colecionador de sonho, eterno adolescente
Vendo meus irmão no palco frente a um mar de gente
Salva-vidas nesse verso, vim do mundo imerso
Contente com o resto, a um passo do caos, sou eu que impeço
Resiliente, disperso, é complexo
Dividindo no bote, sorte é me conter com esse excesso
Salva-vidas nesse verso, vim do mundo imerso
Contente com o resto

E quando a mente do poeta começa a desabar
Não pare de tentar
Que que eu vou fazer se eu desafinar?
Como eu vou saber sem me desafiar?
Eu vou desaparecer
Um tempo pra espairecer
Pra que eu possa renascer, reacender
Eu tive um sonho um dia
E olha que eu nem dormia, ah
Eu tive um sonho um dia
Um sonho que só acordado se cria

Não é ficção, faz parte da realidade do dia a dia
Já aconteceu com o mundo, por aí tu entende a rebeldia
Eu sou efeito colateral desse mundo nojento
Daria um filme
A mulher e uma criança nos braços
Confiando outra vez nos homens errados
Com certeza sente o gosto amargo da frustração
Foi difícil me enganar e dizer que não
E eu não tô aqui pela minha ética moral
Com seis anos, já me vejo olhando pro mal
A primeira tentativa de assédio sexual
Eu sofri nessa dança, se foi a inocência da criança
Nove anos sinto outra tentativa novamente
Combustível de um homem doente
Mas doutor, por favor, sinto culpa memo acontecendo nada
Já não sinto há muito tempo a alma lavada
Veja bem, Rafael, você é só mais um refém
Ele disse: A tentativa já formou minha cicatriz
Incurável, basta só se acostumar com o dia a dia
Por aí tu compreende a rebeldia, ódio do mundo
E eu não tô aqui pra falar de história triste, mas sim da realidade
O que acontece na minha e na sua cidade
Quase aconteceu comigo e já gerou uma revolta
Tudo cor de cinza à minha volta
Fique de olho em nossas crianças, abusadores por todos os lados
Por aí tu já imagina o quadro
Pedro Qualy, obrigado por me tirar do mundo escuro e de ódio
Efeito colateral, SPVIC já entende legal
Nunca se sinta culpado por serem uma vítima da maldade
Mesmo sabendo que essas palavras só ficam na metade
E pra quem me salvou, retribuo pescando almas no esgoto
Porque quem salva uma vida salva o mundo todo

Eu vim pra desconstruir
A multidão se sente só, uh

snippet.title: So endet Corona
snippet.description:
Wann können wir uns wieder in knallvollen Bars in den Armen liegen und laut singen?
Ein wissenschaftlicher Ausblick auf das Ende der Pandemie - und das Leben danach.

INHALT

0:00 Intro
0:58 Herdenimmunität revisited
4:51 It ain’t over till it’s over
6:38 Die Impfungen könnten VORERST weniger ändern als erwartet
7:36 Die Sache mit der sterilisierenden Immunität
9:57 Nach der Pandemie ist vor der Endemie
14:09 Wie ein tödliches Virus zur harmlosen Erkältung werden kann
17:08 Was “Mit Corona leben” wirklich bedeutet

maiLab wird produziert von Mai Thi Nguyen-Kim für funk (ARD & ZDF)
►funk Web-App: https://go.funk.net   
►https://go.funk.net/impressum 


QUELLEN & WEITERE INFOS
(In chronologischer Reihenfolge bezogen aufs Video)

Wir wollten kein Datum abschätzen, aber unsere Kollegen von der Süddeutschen haben dazu ein cooles Tool erstellt, dass eine Monatsschätzung abgibt, wann man - in etwa (!) - mit seiner eigenen Impfung rechnen kann:
https://projekte.sueddeutsche.de/artikel/wissen/corona-impfung-wann-bekommen-sie-einen-impftermin-e292245/ 

Unser maiLab-Video “Corona geht gerade erst los”, das am 1.4.2020 aufgenommen wurde:
https://youtu.be/3z0gnXgK8Do

Das Robert-Koch-Institut RKI spricht von einer Basisreproduktionzahl R0 von 3,3 - 3,8:
https://www.rki.de/DE/Content/Infekt/EpidBull/Archiv/2021/Ausgaben/02_21.pdf?__blob=publicationFile (Epidemiologisches Bulletin vom 14. Januar 2021, siehe Seite 10)

Laut Situationsbericht des RKI liegt die Ansteckungsrate (Reproduktionszahl) mit dem Coronavirus in Deutschland aktuell bei 1,01 (7-Tage-R-Wert, Stand: 24. Januar 2021):
https://www.bundesregierung.de/breg-de/themen/coronavirus/fallzahlen-coronavirus-1738210#:~:text=Laut%20Situationsbericht%20des%20RKI%20liegt,19%2DInfizierter%20im%20Durchschnitt%20angesteckt 

Allgemeines zur Herdenimmunität:
Paul Fine, Ken Eames, David L. Heymann, “Herd Immunity”: A Rough Guide, Clinical Infectious Diseases, Volume 52, Issue 7, 1 April 2011, Pages 911–916, https://doi.org/10.1093/cid/cir007 

Eingeblendete Artikel zu neuen Coronavirus-Mutationen:
https://www.zeit.de/wissen/2021-01/corona-variante-b-1-1-7-mutation-gefahr-massnahmen-angela-merkel
https://www.rbb24.de/panorama/thema/corona/beitraege/2021/01/berlin-vivantes-humboldt-mutation-b117-neue-faelle.html
https://www.spiegel.de/wissenschaft/medizin/corona-nachweis-von-mutationen-in-muenchen-haeufen-sich-mehr-ansteckungen-in-deutschland-a-66cfb83e-2ad0-44b3-a4f2-c6f3398890eb
https://www.sueddeutsche.de/politik/berlin-humboldt-klinikum-b117-coronavirus-mutation-1.5184315

Da wir die Dispersions (Stichwort Superspreader) nur kurz angesprochen haben, hier ein guter Übersichtsartikel von Quarks:
https://www.quarks.de/gesundheit/wie-superspreader-die-pandemie-beeinflussen/
… oder wer lieber ein 5 Minuten- Quarks-Video mit Mai schauen will, hier: https://www.ardmediathek.de/wdr/video/quarks-corona-in-5-minuten/welche-rolle-spielen-superspreader/wdr-fernsehen/Y3JpZDovL3dkci5kZS9CZWl0cmFnLTNjOTY2NWZmLTkzZjEtNGEzOS1hZjg5LWNkZDFiNTA2YTRhZA/

Eingeblendeter Artikel über Heinsberg: https://www.mainpost.de/ueberregional/politik/brennpunkte/coronavirus-karneval-war-wie-ein-brandbeschleuniger-art-10417142

Whoops - Whoopsie! Screen Rant, Pitch Meetings:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZKctcTr6GDc&list=PL--PgETgAz5FGoatB9KQzbnpv0bgZqU2l

Impfgruppen nach Priorität im Epidemiologisches Bulletin vom RKI (14. Janur 2021), siehe Tabelle auf S. 4:
https://www.rki.de/DE/Content/Infekt/EpidBull/Archiv/2021/Ausgaben/02_21.pdf?__blob=publicationFile 

Danke an Prof. Dr. Sandra Ciesek, Direktorin des Instituts für Medizinische Virologie an der Uniklinik Frankfurt für das Gespräch!
Das Coronavirus-Update von NDR Info mit Christian Drosten & Sandra Ciesek: https://www.ndr.de/nachrichten/info/podcast4684.html

Wissenschaftliches Paper über den Weg des SARS-CoV-2 vom tödlichen Pandemie-Virus zur harmlosen Erkältung (Vergleich mit SARS-1, MERS und den endemischen Coronaerkältungsviren)
Lavine, J. S., Bjornstad, O. N., & Antia, R. (2021). Immunological characteristics govern the transition of COVID-19 to endemicity. Science.
DOI: 10.1126/science.abe6522 
https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2021/01/11/science.abe6522 


Eingeblendeter Artikel zur No-Covid-Strategie: https://www.zeit.de/wissen/gesundheit/2021-01/no-covid-strategie-coronavirus-initiative-lockdown

Anmerkung zu “Entweder man wird geimpft oder man steckt sich an” - es gibt Ausnahmen, also Menschen, die aus medizinischen Gründen, z.B. genetische Prädisposition, gar nicht anfällig für das Virus sein könnten und sich grundsätzlich nicht anstecken. Diese Ausnahmen haben wir vereinfachend im Video vernachlässigt.

Dass sich Kinder zum ersten Mal zwischen 3-5 Jahren zum ersten Mal mit den endemischen Coronaviren infizieren, stammt aus dem oben erwähnten Science-Paper: DOI: 10.1126/science.abe6522 
https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2021/01/11/science.abe6522 
(Dieses Paper und die Figure 3B werden im Video eingeblendet)

snippet.title: LEGO® mahnt „Held der Steine“ ab: Muss er jetzt alle Videos löschen? | Anwalt Christian Solmecke
snippet.description:
Der Held der Steine, Thomas Panke, hat 2021 erneut von der Lego Juris A/S ein Abmahnschreiben erhalten. Er solle zahlreiche Videos offline nehmen, in denen er die Marke Lego unberechtigt nutze, in dem er Klemmbausteine anderer Unternehmen als Legosteine benenne. Alle Infos erfahrt ihr im Video.

Hier geht es zum Video vom Held der Steine: https://youtu.be/FpQF-YlXN0o

00:00 Intro
03:03 Was hat Lego vom „Held der Steine“ gefordert?
04:18 Ist eine kurze Frist zur Reaktion ok?
06:41 Warum wurde „Held der Steine“ abgemahnt?
08:55 Lego als Begriff für alle Klemmbausteine: Muss also nicht vielmehr Lego als Marke gelöscht werden?
15:14 Liegt Markenrechtsverletzung vor? Handelt Held der Steine privat oder gewerblich?
17:49 Was tun bei einer Lego-Abmahnung?


Rechtsanwalt Christian Solmecke
Christian Solmecke hat sich als Rechtsanwalt und Partner der Kölner Medienrechtskanzlei WILDE BEUGER SOLMECKE auf die Beratung der Internet-, IT- und Medienbranche spezialisiert. So hat er in den vergangenen Jahren den Bereich Internetrecht/E-Commerce der Kanzlei stetig ausgebaut und betreut zahlreiche Medienschaffende, Web 2.0 Plattformen und App-Entwickler.
Neben seiner Kanzleitätigkeit ist Solmecke Geschäftsführer des Deutschen Instituts für Kommunikation und Recht im Internet an der Cologne Business School (http://www.dikri.de). Dort beschäftigt er sich insbesondere mit den Rechtsfragen in Sozialen Netzen. Vor seiner Tätigkeit als Anwalt arbeitete er über 10 Jahre als freier Journalist und Radiomoderator (u.a. für den Westdeutschen Rundfunk).

snippet.title: Danny MacAskill - The Slabs
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more: https://www.youtube.com/dannymacaskill?sub_confirmation=1

A Danny MacAskill film by Peny - https://www.wearepeny.com/  

With many of our overseas filming plans cancelled as a result of recent times myself and the crew decided to look a little closer to home for our latest film. 

I am a big fan of rock climbing and have been inspired by the various men and woman who set new routes and test themselves on some amazing faces around the world so I set out to find some challenging Slab Rock routes on my home Island of Skye with an aim to ride them in a continuous line and test what was possible on my bike. The remote Dubh Slabs rising out of Loch Coruisk in the heart of the Black Cuilin ridge provided some of the steepest terrain I have ever ridden as well as an amazing back drop for the film. 

The remote location and steep face forced us to think outside the box and meant we had to move away from traditional filming techniques, with us opting to shoot the entire film using GoPros mounted on myself and an FPV (First Person View) racing drone.

Music: 
Arcade Fire - No Cars Go: https://youtu.be/WaIRsqjzsKo

snippet.title: 5 Fakten, die ihr über Auschwitz wissen solltet | Terra X
snippet.description:
Das Vernichtungslager Auschwitz – Endstation für über eine Million Menschen. Wir haben Euch in diesem Video 5 Fakten zusammengefasst, die ihr über Auschwitz wissen solltet: Auschwitz hat Vorläufer. Seit Beginn des Dritten Reiches entstehen überall in Deutschland so genannte Konzentrationslager, kurz KZ, in denen politische Gegner inhaftiert werden. Im Mai 1940 wird in Auschwitz ein weiteres KZ gegründet. Der Ort liegt in Oberschlesien, das nach dem Sieg über Polen von Deutschland annektiert wurde. Die SS, Adolf Hitlers Terrortruppe, nutzt hierzu eine ehemalige polnische Kaserne, die nach bewährtem Muster umgebaut wird. Ein Jahr später, 1941, lässt der Führer der SS, Heinrich Himmler in Auschwitz ein weiteres Lager bauen. Es liegt drei Kilometer entfernt vom bereits bestehenden KZ, das nun Stammlager genannt wird, beim Dorf Brzezinka, das die Deutschen Birkenau nennen. Das Lager wird daher Auschwitz-Birkenau oder Auschwitz 2 genannt. Hier entsteht eine Architektur des Mordes. Die SS organisiert die Vernichtung von Menschen mit industrieller Perfektion: Die Opfer werden per Zug ins Lager deportiert. Ab Frühjahr 1944 führen die Bahngleise bis in den Lagerkomplex hinein. So können die Deportierten direkt im Zielort in Empfang genommen werden. SS-Ärzte teilen die Ankommenden auf der Rampe in arbeitsfähig und nicht-arbeitsfähig ein. Alte, Kranke und Kinder gelten grundsätzlich als nicht-arbeitsfähig. Nach der „Aussortierung“ werden die Opfer zum Duschen geschickt. Die Duschköpfe an der Decke sind Attrappen. Entscheidend sind die umgitterten Käfige, die vom Boden zu einer Luke in der Decke reichen. Es sind Einwurfschächte für das Gift Zyklon B. Rund 30 Minuten dauert der Todeskampf der Menschen. Danach werden ihre Leichen von der Gaskammer zu den Öfen gebracht, wo sie verbrannt werden. Alles ist unter einem Dach – eine systematische Vernichtung. Für diejenigen, die bei der Ankunft nicht „aussortiert“ werden, beginnt die Zwangsarbeit, manche von ihnen werden an die deutsche Kriegsindustrie verkauft. Die Opfer werden nicht nur ermordet und ausgebeutet. Sie werden auch beraubt. Ihr letztes Eigentum wird erst in riesigen Mengen gesammelt und sortiert. Danach wird es in Zügen nach Deutschland geschickt und dort verwertet. Anfang 1945 steht Deutschland kurz vor der Niederlage. Am 27. Januar  befreien Sowjetsoldaten das Lager kampflos. Sie finden grauenvolle Beweise des Verbrechens, die die Täter vor ihrer Flucht nicht beseitigen konnten. Und sie stoßen auf lebende Zeugen: 6000 entkräftete Häftlinge, die die SS bei ihrer Flucht zurückgelassen hat. Die Erinnerung an das Grauen von Auschwitz bleibt in den Überlebenden lebendig, bis heute. 

Dieses Video ist eine Produktion des ZDF.

Abonnieren? Einfach hier klicken – https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCA3mpqm67CpJ13YfA8qAnow?sub_confirmation=1

Alle Filme und Infos zu Terra X gibt es hier – https://terra-x.zdf.de/#xtor=CS3-82

snippet.title: Eriksen löst Halbfinalticket per Traumfreistoß: Inter – Milan 2:1 | Coppa Italia | DAZN Highlights
snippet.description:
Im Viertelfinale der Coppa Italia treffen Tabellenplatz 1 & 2 aufeinander. Für Milan begann die Partie sehr gut und Ibra brachte die Rossoneri nach einer guten halben Stunde in Führung. Im zweiten Durchgang musste Milans Topstar jedoch nach einer Dummheit mit Gelb-Rot vom Platz. Danach ging es für das Team von Pioli bergab. Nach dem Lukaku in der 71. Minute den Ball gegen die Unterlatte donnert und dieser anschließend in den Maschen einschlägt, ist es Eriksen der in der 97. Minute per Traumfreistoß das Derby für Inter entscheidet.

snippet.title: Tabuthema Genitalverstümmelung: Sie bricht das Schweigen I reporter
snippet.description:
⚠️ TRIGGERWARNUNG: In diesem Film geht es um weibliche Genitalverstümmelung. 

👩 Was Sophia (Name von der Redaktion geändert) in ihrer Heimat in Westafrika erlebt hat, ist unglaublich und grausam. Als sie 15 Jahre alt ist, lässt ihr Onkel sie verstümmeln: Ihr wird die Klitoris herausgeschnitten. Erst in Deutschland und erst viele Jahre später kann Sophia darüber sprechen und beginnen, das Trauma zu verarbeiten. Ein mutiger Schritt, denn damit bricht sie ein großes Tabu. 
Weltweit wird schätzungsweise alle 11 Sekunden ein Mädchen an den Genitalien verstümmelt (Quelle: Unicef 2014), mindestens 200 Millionen Frauen sind betroffen (Quelle: WHO 2020).

🎶 Musik:
Clive Martinez – Abscess
London Grammar – Bittersweet Symphony
Clive Martinez – Good night nurse Elkins
Clive Martinez – Placental Repair 
Birdy – People help the People 

🆘 Hilfsangebote
Hilfetelefon Gewalt gegen Frauen: 08000 116 016
Mama Afrika e.V.: https://mama-afrika.org/
Stop mutilation e.V.: http://stop-mutilation.org/beratungsstelle/
Nala e.V.: https://www.nala-fgm.de/

ℹ️ Begrifflichkeiten
Entwicklungsorganisationen und Aktivist:innen sprechen bei Mädchen und Frauen konsequent von "Genitalverstümmelung“. Diese Praktik sei nicht mit der "Beschneidung" bei Jungen oder Männern, also der Entfernung der Penis-Vorhaut, vergleichbar. Für das Gespräch mit Betroffenen wird empfohlen, aus Respekt den Begriff "Beschneidung" zu verwenden. Dafür haben wir uns auch in unserem Film entschieden. 
https://bit.ly/3j6v8MF

💡 Typen der Verstümmelung und Folgen
Die WHO unterscheidet mehrere Typen der weiblichen Genitalverstümmelung: von der Abtrennung des sichtbaren Teils der Klitoris über die Entfernung der Schamlippen bis hin zum Zunähen der Vagina. Der "Eingriff" findet in der Regel ohne Betäubung statt und wird oft mit einer Rasierklinge oder Scherbe durchgeführt. Immer wieder sterben dabei Mädchen, etwa weil sie verbluten. Zu den körperlichen Folgen zählen Schmerzen bei Wasserlassen, Menstruation und Geschlechtsverkehr, Unfruchtbarkeit, Komplikationen bei Schwangerschaft und Geburt. Seelische Folgen können etwa Depressionen oder Angstzustände sein.
https://bit.ly/3t7TwlE

ℹ️  Kultureller Hintergrund
Genitalverstümmelung bei Mädchen und Frauen wird in 30 Ländern in Afrika, dem mittleren Osten und Asien praktiziert. Gerechtfertigt wird die grausame Praktik ganz unterschiedlich. Für viele bedeutet sie den Eintritt ins Erwachsenenalter, das "Frau werden". Mit Religion hat diese Praktik übrigens nicht unmittelbar was zu tun, denn mit 5.000 Jahren ist sie schon wesentlich älter, als der Islam oder das Christentum.
https://bit.ly/3psvWxD

🤕Betroffene in Deutschland
Geschätzt leben in Deutschland rund 70.000 Betroffene, die Dunkelziffer dürfte noch höher sein. Die Zahlen sind in den vergangenen Jahren auf Grund von Einwanderung aus den betreffenden Ländern deutlich gestiegen. In Deutschland ist die Verstümmelung laut §226a StGB verboten und kann mit bis zu 15 Jahren Haft bestraft werden. Doch auch hier sind Mädchen durch die sogenannte "Ferienbeschneidung" bedroht: Sie werden dafür zurück in ihre Heimat geschickt.
https://bit.ly/2Myk6U8

⚕️ OP-Möglichkeiten und -Methoden
Die medizinischen Möglichkeiten reichen von einer Wiederöffnung der Vagina bis hin zu komplexen plastischen Operationen, deren Ziel eine Rekonstruktion der Geschlechtsteile und die Wiederherstellung der Empfindungen ist. 

➡️ Luisenhospital Aachen, Dr.med. Dan O’Dey: 
https://www.luisenhospital.de/luisenhospital-aachen/kliniken/plastische-chirurgie/handchirurgie
➡️ Desert Flower Center, Berlin: https://www.dfc-waldfriede.de/

🎞  Team: Anna van Doorn, Gregor Simbruner, Jakob Gross, Johannes Weuthen, Nele Balgo, Andreas Josef, Benjamin Imort, Lisa Schöffel und Julia von Cube

👉 Ihr findet uns auch hier: 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/reporter
Facebook: http://facebook.com/reporter.offiziell/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/reporter.offiziell/
Snapchat: https://www.snapchat.com/discover/Reporter/3246991136

👉 #reporter gehört zu #funk:
YouTube: http://youtube.com/funkofficial
funk Web-App: http://go.funk.net
Facebook: http://facebook.com/funk
Erlebt mit uns echte Storys. Nah dran. Kritisch. Ohne Filter. 💙 
Jede Woche ein neues Thema 🎥

🙋🏼 Anna ist seit Oktober 2020 Teil des reporter-Teams. Sie hat Medien- und Religionswissenschaften und Journalismus studiert und anschließend die RTL-Journalistenschule absolviert. snippet.localized.title: Tabuthema Genitalverstümmelung: Sie bricht das Schweigen I reporter
snippet.localized.description:
⚠️ TRIGGERWARNUNG: In diesem Film geht es um weibliche Genitalverstümmelung. 

👩 Was Sophia (Name von der Redaktion geändert) in ihrer Heimat in Westafrika erlebt hat, ist unglaublich und grausam. Als sie 15 Jahre alt ist, lässt ihr Onkel sie verstümmeln: Ihr wird die Klitoris herausgeschnitten. Erst in Deutschland und erst viele Jahre später kann Sophia darüber sprechen und beginnen, das Trauma zu verarbeiten. Ein mutiger Schritt, denn damit bricht sie ein großes Tabu. 
Weltweit wird schätzungsweise alle 11 Sekunden ein Mädchen an den Genitalien verstümmelt (Quelle: Unicef 2014), mindestens 200 Millionen Frauen sind betroffen (Quelle: WHO 2020).

🎶 Musik:
Clive Martinez – Abscess
London Grammar – Bittersweet Symphony
Clive Martinez – Good night nurse Elkins
Clive Martinez – Placental Repair 
Birdy – People help the People 

🆘 Hilfsangebote
Hilfetelefon Gewalt gegen Frauen: 08000 116 016
Mama Afrika e.V.: https://mama-afrika.org/
Stop mutilation e.V.: http://stop-mutilation.org/beratungsstelle/
Nala e.V.: https://www.nala-fgm.de/

ℹ️ Begrifflichkeiten
Entwicklungsorganisationen und Aktivist:innen sprechen bei Mädchen und Frauen konsequent von "Genitalverstümmelung“. Diese Praktik sei nicht mit der "Beschneidung" bei Jungen oder Männern, also der Entfernung der Penis-Vorhaut, vergleichbar. Für das Gespräch mit Betroffenen wird empfohlen, aus Respekt den Begriff "Beschneidung" zu verwenden. Dafür haben wir uns auch in unserem Film entschieden. 
https://bit.ly/3j6v8MF

💡 Typen der Verstümmelung und Folgen
Die WHO unterscheidet mehrere Typen der weiblichen Genitalverstümmelung: von der Abtrennung des sichtbaren Teils der Klitoris über die Entfernung der Schamlippen bis hin zum Zunähen der Vagina. Der "Eingriff" findet in der Regel ohne Betäubung statt und wird oft mit einer Rasierklinge oder Scherbe durchgeführt. Immer wieder sterben dabei Mädchen, etwa weil sie verbluten. Zu den körperlichen Folgen zählen Schmerzen bei Wasserlassen, Menstruation und Geschlechtsverkehr, Unfruchtbarkeit, Komplikationen bei Schwangerschaft und Geburt. Seelische Folgen können etwa Depressionen oder Angstzustände sein.
https://bit.ly/3t7TwlE

ℹ️  Kultureller Hintergrund
Genitalverstümmelung bei Mädchen und Frauen wird in 30 Ländern in Afrika, dem mittleren Osten und Asien praktiziert. Gerechtfertigt wird die grausame Praktik ganz unterschiedlich. Für viele bedeutet sie den Eintritt ins Erwachsenenalter, das "Frau werden". Mit Religion hat diese Praktik übrigens nicht unmittelbar was zu tun, denn mit 5.000 Jahren ist sie schon wesentlich älter, als der Islam oder das Christentum.
https://bit.ly/3psvWxD

🤕Betroffene in Deutschland
Geschätzt leben in Deutschland rund 70.000 Betroffene, die Dunkelziffer dürfte noch höher sein. Die Zahlen sind in den vergangenen Jahren auf Grund von Einwanderung aus den betreffenden Ländern deutlich gestiegen. In Deutschland ist die Verstümmelung laut §226a StGB verboten und kann mit bis zu 15 Jahren Haft bestraft werden. Doch auch hier sind Mädchen durch die sogenannte "Ferienbeschneidung" bedroht: Sie werden dafür zurück in ihre Heimat geschickt.
https://bit.ly/2Myk6U8

⚕️ OP-Möglichkeiten und -Methoden
Die medizinischen Möglichkeiten reichen von einer Wiederöffnung der Vagina bis hin zu komplexen plastischen Operationen, deren Ziel eine Rekonstruktion der Geschlechtsteile und die Wiederherstellung der Empfindungen ist. 

➡️ Luisenhospital Aachen, Dr.med. Dan O’Dey: 
https://www.luisenhospital.de/luisenhospital-aachen/kliniken/plastische-chirurgie/handchirurgie
➡️ Desert Flower Center, Berlin: https://www.dfc-waldfriede.de/

snippet.title: Meine Geschwister sterben: Johannes über den Tod
snippet.description:
Richtigstellung: In der Grafik bei 13:16 steht, dass Philipps zweite Chemotherapie erfolgreich war. Tatsächlich hat er aber im Rahmen einer Studie eine zweite Chemotherapie abgebrochen, den Krebs aber trotzdem vorerst besiegt. Hier ist uns in der Redaktion ein Fehler passiert. Tut uns sehr leid!

Philipp und Johannes sind Zwillingsbrüder und YouTuber. Als “The Real Life Guys” machen sie normalerweise krasse DIY-Videos. Sie bauen selber U-Boote, Fluggeräte oder Baumhäuser. Doch in ihren Videos erzählen die beiden auch von privaten Schicksalsschlägen. Vor zwei Jahren starb ihre kleine Schwester. Und jetzt ist Philipp zum dritten Mal so schwer an Krebs erkrankt, dass die Ärzt*innen sagen, er könne jeden Tag sterben. Wie geht Johannes damit um, dass er womöglich auch noch seinen Bruder verliert? Aminata trifft ihn für follow me.reports und spricht mit ihm über diese unglaublich schwierige Situation. Von Geburt an hat Johannes immer alles mit Philipp zusammen gemacht, doch jetzt muss er sich die Frage stellen: Was, wenn mein Bruder nicht mehr da ist?

snippet.title: Ruckrede 2021: 96 Millionen $ Clown spricht zum Volk | ZDF Magazin Royale
snippet.description:
Hier die ganze Sendung schauen: https://kurz.zdf.de/zmr7yt/

We're back, Bitches! Denn so geil wie jetzt war es noch nie. So geil, dass Christian-Drosten-Ultras regelrecht dauererregt sind bei so vielen unterschiedlichen Pandemiestrategien. Alle hängen nur noch in der Wohnung ab, zocken Candy Crush oder hinterlassen einen fetten ökologischen Fußabdruck durch sinnlose Amazon-Bestellungen - familiäre Nervenzusammenbrüche inklusive. Wird also allerhöchste Seehofersche Eisenbahn für ein paar Antikörper gegen schlechte Laune - nicht dass Jan Böhmermann es bei seinen 96 Millionen Dollar Einkommen im Januar noch nötig hätte…
Gebt dem Mutantenvirus keinen Wirt, bleibt ab den 29. Januar jeden Freitag um 23 Uhr auf dem Sofa und schaltet das ZDF Magazin Royale ein. Interessiert euch nicht? WHO CARES! Ab nach Clubhausen mit euch.

Das ZDF Magazin Royale - jeden Freitag ab 20:00 Uhr auf http://zdfmagazinroyale.de und um 23 Uhr in ZDF.

snippet.localized.description:

snippet.title: Anne Frank – so entstand ihr Tagebuch
snippet.description:
#AnneFrank: Urheberin des wohl berühmtesten Tagebuchs der Welt. Das Buch, das sie zwischen 1942 und 1944 schreibt, ist bis heute ein Beststeller. Doch Anne Frank hat ihre Geschichte nicht zu Ende erzählen können, sie wurde als Jüdin von den Nazis verfolgt, gequält, deportiert und ist im Konzentrationslager Bergen-Belsen leidvoll gestorben. Ihr Tagebuch offenbart uns schonungslos die Gedanken eines über Jahre in Todesangst lebenden jungen Mädchens – ohne dass wir dem Schrecken zumindest teilweise entfliehen können. Denn das Tagebuch erzählt keine Geschichte, die auf Tatsachen beruht, sondern die Geschichte von Anne Frank, die so real und wahr ist, wie die Gedanken eben sind, die man seinem geheimen Tagebuch anvertraut. So wurde das Buch in über 70 Sprachen übersetzt und Generationen von Schülerinnen und Schüler in aller Welt haben es gelesen. Wer war diese talentierte junge Frau? Wer war Anne Frank?  

In diesem Video gibt Mirko Antworten auf die Fragen. Er folgt der Spur von Anne und ihrer Familie: Wie sie 1933 das nationalsozialistische Deutschland verlassen und in die Niederlande fliehen, wo Anne ihre Jugend verbringt. Er erklärt, wie Anne zum Tagebuch-Schreiben kommt und wie sie den Zweiten Weltkrieg in Amsterdam erlebt. Natürlich geht es auch darum, wie das Tagebuch gefunden wurde  – und warum das Tagebuch so ein wichtiges Zeitdokument ist.  

Wer mehr über die historischen Hintergründe des Holocaust wissen möchte, findet hier ein Video der Kolleginnen und Kollegen von Terra X:  https://youtu.be/MzuINEWS2sk

Hier findest Du unsere Playlist zum Nationalsozialismus: https://www.youtube.com/watchv=ErSO_z2SYtE&list=PLAo_j4319gfyc0AaibC7yOHX_Ar1gCdAz 

Schau gerne bei Instagram vorbei: https://www.instagram.com/mrwissen2go​...

snippet.title: ich habe mit KARL ESS telefoniert (seinem Team)
snippet.description:
Das war unangenehm! Dirk hat den Check gemacht und bei Karl Ess und seinem Life Building Team angerufen. Karl Ess hat viel Geld und möchte mehr Leuten die Möglichkeit geben ebenfalls viel Geld zu verdienen. Er will wissen, ob Karl Ess und die Life Building Education GmbH nur auf billige Abzocke aus sind oder ob es seriös zugeht. Was passiert in so einem Telefongespräch eigentlich? 

Dirk übernimmt für Hazel Pocket Money und will in seinem ersten eigenen Video wissen, ob Karl Ess und sein Team ihn am Telefon zu einem Vertrag drängen wollen. Ein erster Anruf bei dem Team der Digital Scaling Agency ist Voraussetzung. Am Telefon wollen Karl Ess und sein Team herausfinden, ob Bewerber das Zeug dazu haben, schnell Geld verdienen zu können. Doch der Scam Alarm ist groß: Der Verbraucherschutz warnt immer wieder vor Abzocke am Telefon. Wie seriös sind die Telefonate der Life Building Education GmbH und was gibt es zu beachten? Pocket Money verrät es! 

Wir haben die Life Building Education GmbH um eine Stellungnahme zu den im Video dargelegten Erkenntnissen gebeten. Eine Stellungnahme der Life Building Education GmbH blieb Stand Videoveröffentlichung aus.

snippet.title: Zoes allerletzter Tanz 💫😞 | Köln 50667 #2039
snippet.description:
Obwohl der Abenteuer-Tag für Zoe und Kevin unvergesslich war, neigt auch dieser sich langsam dem Ende zu. Gemeinsam geben sie sich das Versprechen, dass es eine Sache gibt, die sie auch über den Tod hinaus vereinen wird - ihre Liebe...

Abonniert unseren Kanal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnrvUg5MJWPDSrv_voT7AqA?sub_confirmation=1
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/koeln50667
Schaut euch die kompletten Folgen auf TVNOW an: http://www.tvnow.de/rtl2/koeln-50667
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/koeln50667
Twitter: http://twitter.com/rtl2

„Köln 50667“ ist eine Reality-Soap, die seit 2013 täglich von montags bis freitags im Vorabendprogramm gesendet wird.
